{"tid":2379803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建制區議員見徐英偉　促收回區議會撥款權","createTime":"2021-01-25T12:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T13:37:29.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0c4a0c93bfbd181fa405b0f18735ee2dbb25771f","tid":2379803,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T12:40:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=421610&amp;fbclid=IwAR3b90VddJ-aWIGC9kJdnyMmO4uORPtRnitb_nXvD1Vyt-P2yM2Rw67h8fQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D421610%26fbclid%3DIwAR3b90VddJ-aWIGC9kJdnyMmO4uORPtRnitb_nXvD1Vyt-P2yM2Rw67h8fQ&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=d90d0442\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D421610%26fbclid%3DIwAR3b90VddJ-aWIGC9kJdnyMmO4uORPtRnitb_nXvD1Vyt-P2yM2Rw67h8fQ&h=49f19302\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=421610&amp;fbclid=IwAR3b90VddJ-aWIGC9kJdnyMmO4uORPtRnitb_nXvD1Vyt-P2yM2Rw67h8fQ</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】政府正檢視區議會權力，民建聯與民政事務局局長徐英偉會面，建議政府收回區議會的撥款審批權，又稱徐英偉反應積極及正面。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員(區議會第一)劉國勳：「過去撥(款)地區不同團體，為居民舉辦活動，或者派發民生用品。如果情況長期失衡，政府會考慮重新主導，由政府分配，因為如果給地區，地區不舉辦這些活動、不派發物資，何必要撥款區議會做這些工作？」<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府預計農曆新年後，提交《宣誓及聲明條例》修例，當中會要求區議員宣誓效忠，民建聯收集86名建制派區議員聯署，要求當局研究追溯期並成立小組，監察區議員有否違誓。"},{"pid":"8c6eb7097d52b69fdf1ab9d12655d73893b0aba6","tid":2379803,"uid":53687,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T12:42:39.000Z","msg":"唔係唔撥款，而係唔撥款畀有問題嘅組織喎"},{"pid":"d83312bfed722d72d1b0b4d1ab5f27e8fd792e28","tid":2379803,"uid":271516,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T12:49:24.000Z","msg":"我果區成日都派防疫物資<br />\n好過洗幾十萬搞一天團果啲吸水政棍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f712b51a4e274c36e5dc851fa4d8dd71726d86e","tid":2379803,"uid":49609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T13:03:43.000Z","msg":"多數服從少數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n立法會又唔見係咁嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57bb43c07c8942a3f332a35811415c1bc67d1fc","tid":2379803,"uid":33028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T13:04:38.000Z","msg":"到建制多數就會有返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862532a9cdd58ecc2e46c20c9938321e7e92b140","tid":2379803,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T13:32:07.000Z","msg":"組成制度外議會反制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f4e2313cfc904d8e3ef862eb7f8b5888278826","tid":2379803,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T13:33:08.000Z","msg":"少數派<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f1294558354e37b4f8629f4ca067b89d6570df","tid":2379803,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T13:35:28.000Z","msg":"建議政府收回區議會的議席算啦"},{"pid":"4ae42a8054a0e9b598eb62571a1c508948360ceb","tid":2379803,"uid":179718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T13:37:29.000Z","msg":"不如要求直接撥款俾少數派啦"}]}